WEBVTT

00:00.520 --> 00:05.700
English text using timing of 
German version by Vassago HF! 

00:05.701 --> 00:07.700
Everybody lies once in a while.

00:08.000 --> 00:11.200
Hey Joe. Those mutton chops - 
totally working for you.

00:12.400 --> 00:15.500
Hey. Aww, is that the tie 
Rose picked out for you?

00:15.550 --> 00:16.400
No.

00:16.401 --> 00:19.100
Oh. It's nice.

00:19.200 --> 00:21.399
Or, maybe telling little lies 
isn't so bad.

00:21.400 --> 00:24.850
For example, I should have lied 
and said Rose bought this tie.

00:25.550 --> 00:26.950
Once the black box is activated, 

00:26.951 --> 00:29.500
it can detect any lie 
told by anybody in the room

00:29.501 --> 00:33.200
It analyses speech sound waves and can
identify the distortion in our voices

00:33.201 --> 00:35.100
created by the stress of lying.

00:35.101 --> 00:37.200
And it doesn't work at all!

00:37.401 --> 00:39.000
See, it does work.

00:39.001 --> 00:41.000
I never had any doubt.

00:41.001 --> 00:43.199
OK, I had a small doubt.

00:43.200 --> 00:45.399
OK, every day I am incapacitated by fear. 

00:45.400 --> 00:48.050
I don't know where the magic
comes from and I'm terrified that

00:48.051 --> 00:49.900
one day I'll wake up and it will all be gone.

00:49.901 --> 00:53.250
And I'll end up alone, living in my
brother's basement with his trains. 

00:54.500 --> 00:56.201
Buzz, damn you!

00:56.202 --> 00:58.899
Meanwhile, back at a place of business.

00:58.900 --> 01:00.001
Since we're marketing this 
for the military

01:00.002 --> 01:02.600
we have given this project 
our top level security clearance.

01:02.700 --> 01:04.400
Currently, we're the only people 
who know about it.

01:05.900 --> 01:07.200
Alright! I told my shrink. 

01:07.201 --> 01:09.699
He says it's because I want him 
to think I'm important. 

01:09.700 --> 01:11.900
Let me try.

01:12.050 --> 01:14.250
Every spring, on a remote island,

01:14.251 --> 01:17.600
Sean Connery and I hunt the most
dangerous game: man. 

01:18.900 --> 01:20.500
I've also poisoned one of you. 

01:21.700 --> 01:25.800
And before this day is done, I'm going 
to force two of you to make love. 

01:27.500 --> 01:30.399
Oh my god, I'm dying. I can't breathe.

01:30.400 --> 01:33.199
Good luck you two. Don't let 
the intimacy hurt the friendship.

01:33.200 --> 01:37.199
Relax, I'm lying. I'm able to will
myself to believe whatever I say. 

01:37.200 --> 01:39.099
That's why your machine couldn't tell.

01:39.100 --> 01:42.400
As Veronica has demonstrated with her
alarming mixture of sex and death,

01:42.401 --> 01:44.300
you two need to recalibrate this,

01:44.301 --> 01:46.800
so that even she can't fool it.

01:47.200 --> 01:49.899
Hey, it's my favourite people.

01:49.900 --> 01:53.099
- Chet, what can I do for you sir?
- Actually, I'm here to see Ted. 

01:53.100 --> 01:56.899
Are you and your daughter still up for
miniature golf today with me and Olivia?

01:56.900 --> 01:58.000
Looking forward to it, sir. 

01:58.001 --> 02:00.200
Excellent. I've got my clubs 
and I am going to beat you. 

02:02.501 --> 02:04.201
Oh my, that didn't come out right.

02:04.202 --> 02:07.299
Don't worry, I've never hit anyone 
with a golf club.

02:07.300 --> 02:09.000
At least not on purpose.

02:09.400 --> 02:10.899
Hey what's this fun machine? 

02:10.900 --> 02:12.300
Just a random buzzer.

02:12.600 --> 02:14.299
It's working!

02:14.300 --> 02:17.600
I've got to get back upstairs 
and put some more evil into the world.

02:20.400 --> 02:22.899
What did you think, you're elves 
in the North Pole? 

02:22.900 --> 02:25.100
You know where you work. 

02:28.001 --> 02:30.899
So, you're jetting off for a glamorous
golf game with the boss.

02:30.900 --> 02:34.400
It's hardly glamorous. 
On the final hole you have to putt
the ball into the mouth of a rabbit, 

02:34.401 --> 02:37.000
who for copyright reasons 
is named Shmugs Shmunny.

02:37.001 --> 02:39.199
It's not fair. All you people
with your kids,

02:39.200 --> 02:42.499
palling around after hours, 
networking, advancing your careers. 

02:42.500 --> 02:43.300
And I get left behind, 

02:43.301 --> 02:46.599
just because I don't want to turn
my uterus into a human veal farm.

02:46.600 --> 02:49.499
Well some call it the Miracle of Life,
but OK.

02:49.500 --> 02:52.800
Look, Chet's daughter Olivia and Rose
both go to the Veridian aftercare program 

02:52.801 --> 02:56.399
and they've gotten to be friends.
Like 2 cutlets in a scaloppini. 

02:56.400 --> 02:59.001
So I figured it would be good to get 
some face time with the boss. 

02:59.002 --> 03:02.199
Just be careful, Ted. There's a reason
it's called the kid mafia. 

03:02.200 --> 03:03.299
Because you started calling it that?

03:03.300 --> 03:06.100
