- Ideally.

03:27.300 --> 03:29.400
Well, we could. 
We are her friends. 

03:29.401 --> 03:32.899
Yeah, but does she consider us 
close friends. Close enough 
to let us carry her burdens. 

03:32.900 --> 03:36.199
