to hear everything you're saying.

03:39.300 --> 03:40.950
Hey Linda. How's it going?

03:41.400 --> 03:45.049
My brother smashed up my car 
and I need $5000 to get it fixed.

03:45.050 --> 03:46.800
The company said they wouldn't advance it to me, 

03:46.801 --> 03:50.000
unless I agreed to carry a cloned orangutan to term.

03:50.001 --> 03:52.500
I wouldn't do it. 
Orangutan arms are so long,

03:52.501 --> 03:54.699
