the rest of them.

03:54.700 --> 03:58.600
The last 2 weeks of the pregnancy, they'll
be picking up everything you drop. 

03:58.650 --> 04:00.850
Thank you. 
Finally I have a good reason 

04:00.851 --> 04:03.501
